## ðŸ“‹ Overview

The **Neural DX Cluster** is not just a simple Telnet spot display. It is an analytical engine (written in Python) that connects to the global network, ingests raw data, and processes it via a scoring algorithm to identify **what is interesting right now**.

It replaces endless text lists with a visual dashboard (Maps, Charts, Alerts) inspired by Cyberpunk/Sci-Fi interfaces.

